26
00:00:55,950 --> 00:00:57,690
What happens when that happens?

27
00:00:57,690 --> 00:00:59,940
Somebody logs in with those credentials.

28
00:00:59,940 --> 00:01:03,030
Then, they exploit the blast
radius, they move laterally.

29
00:01:03,030 --> 00:01:05,640
In the cloud, that means going
