30
00:01:05,640 --> 00:01:07,170
or different applications.

31
00:01:07,170 --> 00:01:08,730
They elevate their privileges,

32
00:01:08,730 --> 00:01:11,520
ideally getting access
to an admin account.

33
00:01:11,520 --> 00:01:13,440
They establish persistence,

34
00:01:13,440 --> 00:01:15,630
creating new identities and new accounts,

35
00:01:15,630 --> 00:01:18,390
but the goal is always to get access to

36
00:01:18,390 --> 00:01:21,780
so that they can steal and encrypt data.

37
00:01:21,780 --> 00:01:24,060
The kinds of things being in the wild

38
00:01:24,060 --> 00:01:26,970
